MicroServices
Management:it is responsible for placeing services on nods
ServiceDiscovery:manintains list of services and which nods they are located on and find the endpoints of services
ApiGateWay:entry point for elient and it will forward the call to the appropriate service and to the backend and it might aggregate the result/response from the various services and send it to the clients
Docker:images are used to create container on vm
Asyncronus messaging pattern:Queue 
Circuit Breaker pattern:
Mesaging:apache kafka,Rabbit MQ
publish/subscriber
To scale the appl/for orchastration:kubernetes
Microservice securties:Token,API GAteway